  <description>
    <p>Simple Live is a cross-platform application written with Flutter that allows you to watch
      live streams from various platforms, including Huya, Douyu, Bilibili, and Douyin. It's
      available on Android, iOS, Windows, macOS, Linux, and Android TV.</p>
    <p>
      <em>Note: This app is currently only available in Simplified Chinese.</em>
    </p>
  </description>

